# CLAUDE.md — Home Psychiatrist API

## Project Overview
<!-- Fill this in -->
This is a REST API for a funny retro AI psychiatrist, built with Express, TypeScript, and Google Gemini.
Think 80s home computer "therapy" programs — but powered by a real LLM.

## Key Commands
- `npm run dev` — Start dev server with hot reload
- `npm run test` — Run tests with Vitest
- `npm run lint` — Type-check with TypeScript

## Coding Standards
- Use TypeScript strict mode — no `any` types
- Use Express Router for route organization
- Use interfaces for all request/response shapes
- Gemini API calls go through `gemini-service.ts` — never call the SDK directly from routes or business logic
